premise_source_doc_sentence: Verizon makes AC/DC albums available to download , but for several years the band refused to release their albums on iTunes , as iTunes normally allows downloading of individual tracks ; AC/DC publicly stated , `` Our ... reason is that we honestly believe the songs on any of our albums belong together .
AC/DC Live is the second live album by Australian hard rock band AC/DC , released on 27 October 1992 .

The double album AC/DC Live : 2 CD Collector 's Edition was released a month after the single-disc version , in a slipcased two-disc `` book ''  (  similar in shape to old CD longboxes  )  and containing an AC/DC dollar note .
